ged your thinking. Why do you think â€œrhetoricâ€ is considered a threshold concept in writing studies? Pick one vocabulary term that interests youâ€”what do you think it means? âœ… Final Step End your doc with 1â€“2 questions you still have about rhetoric or threshold concepts.	2025-09-08 11:21:21	f	f	\N	241043	202580-Fall 2025-WRDS-1103-048-Wrtng & Inqry Acdmc Ctx I & II
